title: Episode #51: The Defining Decade With Dr. Meg Jay
description: In today's episode I talk to Dr. Meg Jay, a clinical psychologist and author the Defining Decade: Why Your Twenties Matter and How to Make the Most of Them Now. We discuss why your twenties are so important and the challenges that many twentysomethings have today.
author: contact@artofmanliness.com (The Art of Manliness)
